quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  103,0,"Allah - beginning with the name of - the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful."
  103,1,By oath of this era of yours (O dear Prophet Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him).
  103,2,Indeed man is surely in a loss.
  103,3,"Except those who accepted faith, and did good deeds and urged one another to the truth – and urged one another to have patience."
